      "has_children": false,
      "text": "This document summarizes the key performance indicators (KPIs) and metrics that are applied during the annual review process at OptiTech Solutions. It details the performance standards and goals, such as software development project completion rates, code quality benchmarks, marketing campaign ROI, and customer engagement levels. These metrics provide a framework for objective assessment and are used to evaluate the performance of teams and individuals without revealing personal performance data."
